---
---

<section
  class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center px-6 pb-24 pt-24 text-center lg:px-10 lg:pt-32"
>
  <!-- Badge -->
  <div
    class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-border bg-secondary px-3 py-1.5"
  >
    <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
    <span class="font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground">
      Agora com suporte a Ollama →
    </span>
  </div>

  <!-- Headline -->
  <h1
    class="max-w-[900px] text-5xl font-bold leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.04em] text-foreground md:text-6xl lg:text-[4.5rem]"
  >
    Escreva menos.<br />
    Entregue mais.<br />
    <span class="text-primary whitespace-nowrap">Deixa a IA cuidar do PR.</span>
  </h1>

  <!-- Subtext -->
  <p
    class="mt-8 max-w-[560px] text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground md:text-lg"
  >
    CLI tools para gerar descrições de PR e cards de teste no Azure DevOps.
    Suporta OpenRouter, Groq, Gemini e Ollama. Um comando. Zero burocracia.
  </p>

  <!-- CTAs -->
  <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
    <a
      href="#install"
      class="rounded-full bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-foreground transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
    >
      Instalar agora
    </a>
    <a
      href="/docs"
      class="rounded-full border border-border bg-secondary px-6 py-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-foreground"
    >
      Ver documentação →
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Trust -->
  <p class="mt-6 font-mono text-xs text-muted-foreground/60">
    Sem cadastro. Funciona no terminal. Código aberto.
  </p>
</section>
